item.title: Hmmmm, MAC??
item.description: Written by: Thriven. We are all familiar with Apple’s laptop Macbook. For those who aren’t here is a brief idea, MacBook Air, Macbook and MacBook Pro are Apple’s versions of laptop. No one addresses it as a laptop actually, everyone calls it a Mac or Macbook. If you own a Macbook then you just have a Macbook not a laptop. These are really expensive like reaaaalllly expensive, a basic version of Macbook costs around 1 lakh, you want some accessories?
